                <h1>When Was Yeti Founded? Discover the Origins of Yeti Coolers</h1>
                <p>Yeti was founded in 2006 by brothers Roy and Ryan Seiders in Austin, Texas. The brand quickly gained popularity for its high-quality coolers and drinkware designed for outdoor enthusiasts. Yeti's dedication to durability and performance has positioned it as a leader in the premium outdoor gear market.</p>
